product_name: Tissot PRS 516 Chronograph Red Men's Watch
description: The PRS 516 is simply the most prestigious sports watch within the Tissot collection. This timepiece dates back to 1965, featuring design details inspired by classic sports cars including a perforated bracelet and piston-shaped pushers. The PRS 516 is truly a pioneer watch that will never go out of style. All Tissot watches come with 2 year manufacturer's warranty. T100.417.11.051.01

product_name: MIDO Commander Big Date M021.626.33.061.00 - 42 mm
description: The Commander Big Date Swiss watch celebrated the 100th anniversary of the brand in 2018. Its large date aperture at 6 o'clock offers unrivalled date legibility. The sunray satin-finished dial is extremely pure and protected by an elegant round case in satin-finished stainless steel and enhanced by a polished bezel. This anthology and iconic piece is fitted with the Caliber 80, an automatic watch movement that offers up to 80 hours of power reserve. product_name: Tissot Tradition Powermatic 80 Open Heart Men's Watch
description: The beauty of the Powermatic 80 movement with its awesome 80-hour power reserve is revealed by the opening at 12 o'clock on the dial as well as through the transparent case back. The dials feature a subtle grain d’orge pattern in the centre and a smooth outer dial ring housing simple indexes and an oversized XII. Sapphire crystal ensures scratch-resistant protection for the dial and a selection of textured leather straps and metal bracelets completes the highly desirable look. All Tissot watches come with 2 year manufacturer's warranty. T063.907.11.038.00

product_name: Tissot Gentleman Powermatic 80 Open Heart Men's Watch
description: The understated exterior of the Gentleman collection hides the innovation at the heart of the automatic range. The Powermatic 80 movement is even more precise thanks to its silicon balance spring that offers additional resistance to the magnetic fields we encounter in everyday life. Open Heart models in the collection use innovative Nivachron balance springs to the same effect. With 80 hours of power reserve, it’s a movement that can keep pace with busy lifestyles. These Gentleman models are truly an impressive offering. All Tissot watches come with 2 year manufacturer's warranty. T127.407.11.041.01

The Captain Cook High-Tech Ceramic is the culmination of many years of research and development together with the history and tradition of the Rado Captain Cook. The further development of the Captain Cook collection in high-tech ceramic is Rado’s DNA in its purest form. The innovative Nivachron™ hairspring provides an advantage in everyday life by protecting the timepiece from magnetic fields. product_name: Tissot Seastar 1000 Chronograph Black/Silver Men's Watch
description: Impressive water-resistance up to a pressure of 30 bar (300 m/1000 ft) is combined with the energy of a Swiss-made quartz movement. With a screw-down crown and case back, unidirectional safety bezel and Super-LumiNova® ensuring it is readable in the dark, the Seastar 1000 Quartz is an aquatic ace that truly has it all. The screw-down crown also offers additional protection against knocks. A range of sizes and colour combinations ensure the Seastar offers something for everyone. T120.417.11.051.00
